column17:
With this Memory Foam Pillow your sleeping experience will become joyful and refreshing as you don't have to wake up to a stiff neck anymore. This Pillow is perfect for any sleeping position- back side & stomach & supports the cervical vertebra. Its Uses The memory foam pillow is a part of home textiles and furnishing which has one and the ultimate reason of giving you sound sleep for the whole night. The major advantage of memory foam pillows is that they're extremely supportive which makes them a good option for people with back or neck problems. This pillow molds itself around your head and neck ultimately providing you sound sleep. How this stuff work? This memory foam pillow has the ability to uniformly spread the pressure exerted by a body over its surface. Therefore the force applied by it to the body it supports is not focused on a particular area. Moreover it equally supports the whole body. On the other hand the memory foam pillow molds according to the shape of your head and neck ensuring maximum comfort for you. Also you are very much grateful to sleep in the same position for more time in order to maintain the shape of the memory foam pillow. The moment you change your position and the pressure is released memory foam pillow relapses to its original shape and then it again molds according to your new posture.

  • Material: Memory Foam
